"title": "4826: fire",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4826: fire",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture shows fire being used in a variety of ways in this world. Fire is often mentioned as a symbol, denoting God's presence and power, his judgment or his purifying work.</p>\n<h2>Domestic uses of fire</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:11\">ISA 50:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:22\">JER 36:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:15\">MAT 5:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:67\">MRK 14:67</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:55\">LUK 22:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:18\">JHN 18:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:9\">JHN 21:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:2\">ACT 28:2</a></p>\n<h2>Cremation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:12\">1SA 31:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:25\">JOS 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:10\">AMO 6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Fire as an instrument of punishment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:14\">LEV 20:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:24\">GEN 38:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:14\">LEV 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:9\">LEV 21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:49\">JDG 9:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:6\">DAN 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Fire as an instrument of divine judgment</h2>\n<h3>In general terms</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10\">2PE 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24\">GEN 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:2\">LEV 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1\">NUM 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:35\">NUM 16:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7-2Thess1:8\">2TH 1:7–1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal fire</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:14\">ISA 33:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:24\">ISA 66:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:12\">MAT 3:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:17\">LUK 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8\">MAT 18:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43\">MRK 9:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:10-Rev14:11\">REV 14:10–14:11</a></p>\n<h2>Fire used in worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:2\">NUM 28:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:7\">LEV 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:9\">1SA 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:11\">2CH 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:3\">EZR 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>Prayers answered by fire</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:26\">1CH 21:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:38\">1KI 18:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:10\">2KI 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:1\">2CH 7:1</a></p>\n<h2>Symbolic significance of fire</h2>\n<h3>God's presence and power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:2\">EXO 3:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:3\">ACT 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21\">EXO 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:18\">EXO 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:24\">LEV 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:36\">DEU 4:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:21\">JDG 6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:20\">JDG 13:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:11\">2KI 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:3\">PSA 50:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:3\">PSA 97:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:29\">JER 23:29</a></p>\n<h3>Judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1\">MAL 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:24\">DEU 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:15-Isa66:16\">ISA 66:15–66:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:14\">JER 5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:45\">JER 48:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:20\">EZK 22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:4\">AMO 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Purification or refinement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:23\">NUM 31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:10\">ISA 48:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:2\">MAL 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:13\">1CO 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Zeal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:17\">JHN 2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:9\">PSA 69:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:9\">JER 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:32\">LUK 24:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:6\">2TI 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>The power to destroy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:6\">JAS 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:27-Prov6:29\">PRO 6:27–6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:27\">PRO 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:18\">ISA 9:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:2\">ISA 43:2</a></p>",
